#CHIP QSound
#CLOCK 24576000

; QSound (Capcom Arcade) Basic Test — 16-channel synthesis
;
; QSound is Capcom's proprietary audio synthesizer used in arcade systems.
; It supports:
; - 16 simultaneous sound channels
; - FM synthesis
; - PCM sample playback
; - Advanced echo/reverb effects
;
; Tests:
; - All 16 channels
; - Basic melody and harmony
; - Pitch and volume control

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channels 1-4: Lead melody
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r4

; Channels 5-8: Harmony (thirds)
e4 . f4 . g4 . a4 .

r4

; Channels 9-12: Bass line
c3 . . d3 . . e3 . .

r4

; Channels 13-16: Drums/percussion
n4 . . n4 . . n4 . .

r4

r2

#END
